    "name": "S7: SCCS — Statin Exposure and Stroke (Within-Person)",
    "description": "Self-controlled case series analysis evaluating the association between statin exposure and stroke within individual patients. The within-person design eliminates time-invariant confounding by using each patient as their own control, comparing stroke event rates during statin-exposed periods vs unexposed periods within the same individual.",
